Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.570
Ajoyib, hozirda Java
dasturida matnni 

00:00:03.570 --> 00:00:05.170
mahalliylashtirishni tugatdingiz.

00:00:05.170 --> 00:00:08.010
Umid qilamanki, ozgina o‘zgartirishlar 
kiritgan holda, 

00:00:08.010 --> 00:00:10.870
o‘z ilovangizni yangi 
tomoshabinlarga ochishingiz mumkin.

00:00:10.870 --> 00:00:11.918
Keling, bizning 
yechimimizni ko‘rib chiqamiz.

00:00:11.918 --> 00:00:14.410
Bu yerda biz strings.xml fayli bo‘lib,
unda biz ilovadagi barcha 

00:00:14.410 --> 00:00:17.390
mumkin bo‘lgan satrlarni 
chiqarib tashladik.

00:00:17.390 --> 00:00:19.860
Har bir satr manbasi uchun biz
tarjimonga to‘g‘ri tarjimani aniqlashda 

00:00:19.860 --> 00:00:23.300
yordam berish uchun sharh 
va belgilar chegarasini taqdim etamiz.

00:00:25.090 --> 00:00:27.670
Endi bizning tartibimizda 
manbalarga murojaat qilamiz.

00:00:28.710 --> 00:00:31.420
Bizning shablonimizda qattiq kodlash 
satrlari haqida Android Studio 

00:00:31.420 --> 00:00:32.280
tomonidan boshqa 
ogohlantirishlar yo‘q.

00:00:33.290 --> 00:00:36.250
Va bu yerda ularning barcha ispancha 
tarjimalari bilan strings.xml

00:00:36.250 --> 00:00:38.800
faylining ispan versiyasi mavjud.

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:42.060
Agar tarjimalar muharririni ochsangiz,
manbalar nomi, ingliz tilidagi tarjimalar,

00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:46.345
shuningdek ispan tarjimalarini
ko‘rishingiz mumkin.

00:00:46.345 --> 00:00:50.360
Keyin havola faylimizda barcha 
manbalarga murojaat qilishimiz mumkin.

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:53.350
Endi esa Android Studio shablonimizda 
qattiq kodlash satrlari 

00:00:53.350 --> 00:00:54.660
haqida boshqa 
ogohlantirishlar ko‘rsatmaydi.

00:00:54.660 --> 00:00:58.320
Java kodimiz ichida ushbu 
manbalarga ham murojaat qilamiz.

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:02.150
Shuni esda tutingki, bu yerda ushbu 
kod chizig‘i bilan mahalliy valyutani olamiz.

00:01:02.150 --> 00:01:07.020
Bu joriy mahalliy uchun kirish narxini 
joriy c-ga formatlaydigan 

00:01:07.020 --> 00:01:08.190
yordamchi funksiya hisoblanadi.

00:01:08.190 --> 00:01:11.410
Yechimning barcha kodlari quyida 
o‘qituvchi eslatmalarida bog‘langan.

00:01:11.410 --> 00:01:13.610
Ajoyib ish.

00:01:13.610 --> 00:01:16.220
Endi "Android"dagi manbalar bilan yana 
nima qilish mumkinligini 

00:01:16.220 --> 00:01:17.540
batafsilroq ko‘rib chiqamiz.

